      <title>EU Action Plan on Nutrition</title>
      <link>http://knowledge.cta.int/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/EU-Action-Plan-on-Nutrition</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In December 2014, the Council of the European Union endorsed the&lt;a href="http://ec.europa.eu/europeaid/action-plan-nutrition-commission-staff-working-document_en" target="_blank"&gt; EU Action Plan on Nutrition&lt;/a&gt;. This action plan outlines how the Commission plans to reach its commitment to reducing stunting in children under five by at least 10% (7 million children) of the World Health Assembly goal by 2025. The plan addresses how EU’s strategic objectives in the areas of governance, scaled up interventions and research are to be attained, underscoring the need to work more closely with development actors and partner countries. (EU Council, 12/12/2014)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <author>francis@cta.int (Engelhard Rutger )</author>
